Directory for external libraries

* CIF Device Driver

Installation (Linux)
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
1. Download tarball from http://www.hilscher.com/support_software.html ,
   select category Drivers, File DRV-LNX (i.e. CIFV2100.tgz).
   Unpack with tar -xvf CIFV2100.tgz
2. Download and unzip the windows driver (see below) and move file DNM_USER.H
   to cif-v2.100/usr-inc/dnm_user.h
3. Go to cif-v2.100/api
4. Run make (to generate cif_api.o object)
5. Convert cif_user.h and dnm_user.h to UNIX format and apply patches:
   patch cif-v2.100/usr-inc/dnm_user.h dnm_user.h.diff 
   patch cif-v2.100/usr-inc/rcs_user.h rcs_user.h.diff 

Installation (Windows)
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
1. Download installation file from http://www.hilscher.com/support_software.html,
   select section Driver, File DRV-WIN (i.e. cif3113.zip)
2. Unzip with unzip cif3113.zip


* NI-DNET driver

Installation (Windows)
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
1. Download installation file from http://digital.ni.com/softlib.nsf/webcategories/85256410006C055586256BBB002C0F33?opendocument&node=132060_US
2. Start the installation

